  "description": "Inspired by the arcade game <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/xevious\">Xevious</a>, you play the role of a mercenary who has accepted the task of flying over a planets surface in your space craft, consisting of ten levels to face and destroy <i>Point X</i>. In this vertically scrolling shooter you must avoid and shoot waves of alien ships as well as bomb any ground installations with the aid of a sight. Some installations will fire back and if you hit a ship or a bullet then you lose part of a damage bar and when it reaches zero it is game over. The joystick is used to control your ship.",
